        "title": "fix(release): remove appcast entry for unpublished 3.5.3 release",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Removes the v3.5.3 item from `appcast.xml` because no GitHub release asset exists for that tag\n- Sparkle currently offers 3.5.3 to users on 3.5.2, then fails with a 404 when downloading `Peekaboo-3.5.3.app.zip`\n\n## Root cause\nCommit `9b9c5de4` added the appcast entry, but `v3.5.3` was never published as a GitHub release (tag exists, release/asset missing).\n\n## Test plan\n- [x] `xmllint --noout appcast.xml`\n- [ ] After merge, Sparkle check on 3.5.2 reports up to date instead of failing download\n- [ ] When 3.5.3 is actually released, re-add the appcast entry via the normal release script\n\nMade with [Cursor](https://cursor.com)",
